title: Thyme to Eat
description: A warm cafe serving a wide range of vegetarian and vegan food, from breakfast, brunch and lunch daily changing specials, including rustic leek and stilton pie served with new potatoes, braised red cabbage and runner beans. Has an extensive array of gluten free items. In-house-made vegan and gluten free soups available, in addition to in-house-made cakes. Drinks include a range of specialty teas and coffees using soy milk at no extra charge.
